Sure, here are some examples:

1. Oni *pitaju* gde se nalazi restoran. (They are asking where the restaurant is.)
2. Kada će te me *pitati* za savet? (When will you ask me for advice?)
3. Njih dvoje *su pitali* isto pitanje. (The two of them asked the same question.)
4. Da li si *pitao* roditelje za dozvolu? (Did you ask your parents for permission?)
5. Niko neće *pitati* za tvoje mišljenje ako se ne izraziš. (Nobody will ask for your opinion if you don't express it.)
6. *Pitaj* me šta god te zanima. (Ask me anything you're curious about.)
7. Nećeš znati dok me ne *pitaš*. (You won't know until you ask me.)
8. Oni *će pitati* za objašnjenje kada vide grešku. (They will ask for an explanation when they see the mistake.)
9. *Pitali* smo se šta bi bilo da smo izabrali drugačiji put. (We wondered what would have happened if we had chosen a different path.)
10. Ti si *pitao* za savet, a ja sam ti ga dao. (You asked for advice, and I gave it to you.)